snippet.title: Word Factori Steam Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
📢WISHLIST ON STEAM: https://cutt.ly/factoriyt

Word Factori (previously known as factori) is a word-building game where your only resource is the letter "i". Build a chain of factories to bend, rotate, reflect, and merge "i" into more complex letters. Discover secret letter recipes, unlock hidden word art, and optimize your factory chains for high scores.

Coming soon to Steam! https://cutt.ly/factoriyt

Music
Driving Eva by Darkstorm & Diabolik
https://badtaste.bandcamp.com/track/driving-eva
